    <h3 class="subhead">BOHEMIAN RITUAL</h3>
    <p>Meanwhile, the Bohemian (Czech) Ritual of drinking Absinthe has become very popular. You put one or two sugar cubes on an Absinthe spoon and pour Absinthe over it. Then you light up the sugar and wait until the flames caramelize it. The sugar drips into the glass and blends with the Green Fairy. Then water is added to create the Louche. We do not recommend this ritual. The fine taste of the Absinthe is negatively effected by the caramelization of the sugar.</p></div>

