    <h3 class ="subhead">ABSINTHE FOUNTAIN</h3>
    <p>An Absinthe Fountain is an authentic Absinthe accessory which was present in every Absinthe bistro during the time of the Belle Epoque. Out of the spigots water drips on to the Absinthe sugar, dissolves it and blends with the Absinthe to create the perfect louche.</p></div>

