    <h3 class="subhead">BROUILLER AUTOMATIC</h3>
    <p>Instead of an Absinthe fountain you can also use an Absinthe Brouilleur. The water flows over a see saw into the Absinthe while you listen to the mechanical "tic tac" sound of this Absinthe accessory.</p></div>

